Data Attribution

Education data (WCDE v3):
  Lutz, W., Reiter, C., Özdemir, C., Yildiz, D., Guimaraes, R. & Goujon, A.
  (2021). Skills-adjusted Human Capital Shows Increasing Global Progress and
  Persistent Disparities. Nature Human Behaviour, 5, 701–711.
  Wittgenstein Centre for Demography and Global Human Capital (IIASA/VID/WU).
  WCDE Data Explorer: http://www.wittgensteincentre.org/dataexplorer

World Bank indicators (life expectancy, TFR, GDP per capita, CO2):
  World Bank. World Development Indicators. Various years.
  https://datacatalog.worldbank.org/dataset/world-development-indicators
